cdata.name: APIS
cdata.desc:
The APIS is building an Ethereum-based Masternode Mediation Platform to familiarize the term masternode to a larger range of people and to let them enjoy the advantages and benefits of a masternode.The APISmasternode mediation platform enables the entire spectrum of users to have easy access to the two-tier incentivized network, also known as the Masternode Network.

APIS is an ERC20 token that powers the APIS platform.
